W<-rnorm(2000)
X<-numeric(2000)
for(t in 3:2000){
  X[t]<-0.3*X[t-1]+0.5*X[t-2]+W[t]
}
ts.plot(X)

acf(X)

pacf(X)

modelo<-arima(X,order=c(2,0,0))
modelo

P<-3
D<-3
Q<-3
tabla<-data.frame()
for(p in 0:P){
  for(d in 0:D){
    for(q in 0:Q){
      modelo<-arima(X,order=c(p,d,q))
      AIC<-AIC(modelo)
      sbic<-AIC(modelo,k=log(length(X)))
      tabla<-rbind(tabla,c(p,d,q,AIC,sbic))
    }
  }
}
